@node rand, random number
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <stdlib.h>

int rand(void);
@end example

@subheading Description

Returns a pseudo-random number from zero to @code{RAND_MAX}. 

@subheading Return Value

The number.

@subheading Example

@example
/* random pause */
for (i=rand(); i; i--);
@end example

